-- Jorvik profile for cross-compiled unit test targets. Jorvik is a
-- relaxation of Ravenscar that permits Ada.Calendar and other facilities
-- AUnit and the generated test scaffold reach for. Paired with the testing/
-- Safe_Deallocator body so AUnit setup/teardown can free heap-allocated
-- test fixtures.
--
-- Intentionally asymmetric with ravenscar.adc. This file does NOT add
-- pragma Restrictions (No_Unchecked_Deallocation). Production-discipline
-- Jorvik builds (if/when they exist) should pass an additional .adc that
-- layers the restriction back on rather than amending this file.
pragma Profile (Jorvik);
